{"tid":923821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女傭被控色誘　雇主11歲兒：我上癮了...","createTime":"2018-12-01T14:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T16:32:33.000Z","uid":150609,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4787a0699ee18e4d786e849dc7144545c550cc25","tid":923821,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T14:51:37.000Z","msg":"新加坡1名33歲的印度籍女傭A，因涉色誘雇主的11歲兒子，上個月22日被判監18個月。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5af8xyn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5af8xyn.jpg&h=8097fc00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181201/1476757/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181201%2F1476757%2F&d=Jg%2B7rGYuEHm6f31NpujP38PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=0c46de76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181201%2F1476757%2F&h=19835f7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181201/1476757/</a><br />\n<br />\n根據馬來西亞《中國報》報導，A女被控訴在2016年的1-5月間，4次性騷擾/性侵男童，另有1次恐嚇男童，<span style=\"color: gold;\">男童作證時說，他與A女發生性方面的行為之後，就「上癮」了，也怕告訴父母、覺得愧疚，但無法控制自己，還會想要再發生。<br />\n</span><br />\n根據男童敘述：<br />\n2016年1月：<br />\n某日下午A女在2人獨處時，做出淫穢的手勢。<br />\n幾天後，將男童叫進廚房，要男童嘴對嘴親吻她。<br />\n之後親吻升級，兩人躺在男童妹妹床上，A女舌吻男童，並擁抱他。<br />\n<br />\n2016年2月：<br />\nA女找男童親熱，期間脫掉上衣，要男童抓她的胸部。<br />\n<br />\n2016年3月：<br />\nA女脫掉胸罩，要男童捏她的乳首。<br />\n<br />\n2016年5月：<br />\nA女與男童親熱時，伸手撫摸男童的下體。<br />\n<br />\n報導中說，在2016年的7月11日，男童打電話給父親，說A女要打她，男童父親趕回家後，發現2人之間氣氛不對勁，而男童在A女面前顯得很害怕，於是將兒子帶到房中，男童才將上述情事全盤托出。<br />\n<br />\n報導中說，男童還說，2人發生以上行為後，他要求A女倒水給他喝，A女不但不肯，還說手中握有與男童親熱的影片，此後只要2人之間有摩擦，A女就會提醒男童，自己有拍影片，讓男童感到害怕。<br />\n<br />\n面對法院的判決，A女表示不服並且提出上訴，她說，整件事情是男童「先出手」的，男童會問她「有無男友」、「是否曾與男友做愛」等問題，還會擅自闖進她房間，躺在她身上、用腳掀開她睡衣，還會摸她的臉。<br />\n<br />\nA女說，她擔心男童被父親懲罰，所以沒有去投訴，沒想到被男童反咬一口。她也反問，如果真是男童被她性騷擾/性侵，男童的父親知道後，怎麼沒有馬上報警，而是拖了5天？根本不合理。<br />\n<br />\n報導中說，男童父親則是回應說，因為工作繁忙，他與妻子周末才有時間，所以拖了5天「調查來龍去脈」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小孩騎大車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7667ea21c18baf689246b53de43d3bbf94ab5e24","tid":923821,"uid":52652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"人妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1abeac965498a8650b90f8a6f5897f4467236f84","tid":923821,"uid":158585,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T14:54:31.000Z","msg":"11歲就識射精？"},{"pid":"c9f3b9cf504c58001607c3fe80c3f8046ed3583e","tid":923821,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"早熟"},{"pid":"5ab3bff0d6bf2b45769eebd90e7db2298e3286a2","tid":923821,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:02:04.000Z","msg":"估中第一隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4fe39ac192f1d6d933c59094f71fcb138aa23ac","tid":923821,"uid":59795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:05:14.000Z","msg":"老豆唔識玩<br />\n唔係可以父子丼"},{"pid":"17d1ce947dfe94baca193c4d13236b1966e99a70","tid":923821,"uid":200521,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5ab3bff0d6bf2b45769eebd90e7db2298e3286a2","tid":923821,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:02:04.000Z","msg":"估中第一隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:06:58.000Z","msg":"新北市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr